### Lifecycle of Work Items



1. Proposal
2. Adoption
3. Work Item Drafts
4. Closure


### Work Item Process


#### Proposal

Proposals are made by creating a Github issue and announcing the proposal on the CCG email discussion list.

The Github Issue is posted to the CCG community repo [https://github.com/w3c-ccg/community/issues](https://github.com/w3c-ccg/community/issues) by using the “New Work Item” template as follows:



